            <thetext>Specifying the ROOT macro in a custom config.json will still result in a BUILD_PATH of &quot;./build&quot;, although it is originally expressed as BUILD_PATH = &quot;${ROOT}/build&quot;, so the altered ROOT macro should influence it. This is not the case.</thetext>
